name: 10 17 21   TARGET HOUSE WITH PURPLE, YELLOW AND GREEN   NFT- 004 / 5332 X 3999PX
description: I took my first photograph of historic Fort Barry Building T828 (also referred to as the Target House) on July 2, 2015, while I was an affiliate artist at Headlands Center for the Arts. What started as a modest photographic exploration, blossomed in to an unexpected meditation on image, place, memory, time, and ultimately, loss. This project is ongoing.
